ADDITIONAL DISCLAIMER FOR SECURITY-SENSITIVE SYSTEMS:

This software is provided for educational and demonstration purposes. The 
default configuration includes hardcoded credentials and encryption keys that 
are NOT SECURE for production use.

Before deploying this system in any production, commercial, or safety-critical
environment, you MUST:

1. Replace all hardcoded credentials with secure authentication
2. Generate secure random encryption keys and store them safely
3. Implement HTTPS/TLS for all network communications
4. Conduct a thorough security audit
5. Comply with all applicable regulations (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)

The authors and contributors assume NO LIABILITY for any security breaches,
data losses, or damages resulting from deployment of this software without
proper security hardening.

USE AT YOUR OWN RISK.
